# kinsta_wordpress_site (Resource)

Creates and manages a [Kinsta WordPress site](https://kinsta.com/wordpress-hosting/). Site creation is asynchronous and typically takes 1–3 minutes.

~> **Note on immutability:** All fields are `ForceNew`. Any configuration change destroys and recreates the site.

~> **Note on write-only fields:** Admin credentials (`admin_email`, `admin_password`, `admin_user`) and `site_title` are sent on creation but are not returned by the Kinsta API. Terraform preserves these in state but cannot detect out-of-band changes to them.

