## Import

WordPress sites can be imported using the site ID:

```shell
terraform import kinsta_wordpress_site.example <site_id>
```

The site ID is available as the `site_id` attribute after creation, or from the MyKinsta URL:
`https://my.kinsta.com/sites/details/<site_id>/...`
